"9042,""    To begin working with the Fumiguide* Program for ProFume* gas fumigant, go to ""File"" in the Tool Bar above. Select ""New"" if creating a new job, or select ""Open"" to open an existing job.  You may also use the icons in the Tool Bar to do the same. The Fumiguide* Program for ProFume* gas fumigant functions in English and Metric units.    
    Go to ""View"" in the Tool Bar above, select ""Options"".Then select either English or Metric Units.    
    You can change units at any time within a job, by following these same instructions.
    The Fumiguide* Program for ProFume* gas fumigant operates using AM/PM Time, (e.g. 2:35 PM being 14:35
     in military time).  To properly set your computer clock, please see the Help File section ""How to
    Change Region Settings to Display Time Correctly"" or search by the keyword ""Region
    Settings""        """
