10049,"The "Low" option  provides control of larvae, "
10050,"pupae, adults and some eggs.  This base level of control is "
10051,"suited for maintenance fumigations. "
10052,"The "High" option provides control of eggs, larvae, "
10053,"pupae and adults.  This high level of control is suited for "
10054,"heavy-duty clean out fumigations."
10055,"NOTE:  After calculating "low" and "high" dosage, the fumigator can recommend a "
10056,"custom dosage between "low" and "1500 CT" that will meet customer expectations."
